              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10752235-l-a-i-n-e-y-back-in-a-bit?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10752235-l-a-i-n-e-y-back-in-a-bit?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/10752235-l-a-i-n-e-y-back-in-a-bit?shelf=romance-where">romance-where</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2936222208" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6662638294838388293">This is as much a love story as <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8528710.Gone_with_the_Wind' title='Gone with the Wind by Margaret Mitchell' rel='nofollow noopener'>Gone with the Wind</a> was a love story to me...<br/><br/>As in, not at all. <br/><br/>False advertising.</span>
  <span id="freeText6662638294838388293" style="display:none">This is as much a love story as <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8528710.Gone_with_the_Wind" title="Gone with the Wind by Margaret Mitchell" rel="nofollow noopener">Gone with the Wind</a> was a love story to me...<br /><br />As in, not at all. <br /><br />False advertising.</span>
