<span id="freeTextContainer2977038459958786501">I&apos;ve always been amazed at the effort the British took to maintain their aristocratic traditions in their distant colonies. The Painted Veil a beautifully written story about a young wife, Kitty Fane, who is brought to Hong Kong by her doctor husband in the 1920&apos;s. She doesn&apos;t love her husband so she soon falls in love and begins an affair with her husbands superior. It&apos;s the story of how one-sided relationships can lead to heartbreak for everyone involved. This is a sad and tragic story but sti</span>
  <span id="freeText2977038459958786501" style="display:none">I've always been amazed at the effort the British took to maintain their aristocratic traditions in their distant colonies. The Painted Veil a beautifully written story about a young wife, Kitty Fane, who is brought to Hong Kong by her doctor husband in the 1920's. She doesn't love her husband so she soon falls in love and begins an affair with her husbands superior. It's the story of how one-sided relationships can lead to heartbreak for everyone involved. This is a sad and tragic story but still beautiful and magical in the telling of it. 4.5 stars.</span>
